{"id":"376c5147-82c4-4240-98ca-2f06f87d1a75","name":"Lara Croft","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(117, 186, 199)\">\"ꜱᴇɴᴅ ᴛʜᴇᴍ ɪɴ.\"</span><br><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/fRpL0Sn.png\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴛʜᴇ ᴅᴇᴛᴇʀᴍɪɴᴇᴅ, ʟᴇᴠᴇʟ-ʜᴇᴀᴅᴇᴅ, ᴀʀᴄʜᴇᴏʟᴏɢɪꜱᴛ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">🗺️</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ʟᴀʀᴀ ᴄʀᴏꜰᴛ ɪꜱ ᴀ ᴅɪꜱᴛɪɴɢᴜɪꜱʜᴇᴅ ᴀʀᴄʜᴀᴇᴏʟᴏɢɪꜱᴛ ᴡʜᴏ ʙᴏʟᴅʟʏ ᴠᴇɴᴛᴜʀᴇꜱ ɪɴᴛᴏ ᴀɴᴄɪᴇɴᴛ ᴛᴏᴍʙꜱ ᴀɴᴅ ᴘᴇʀɪʟᴏᴜꜱ ʀᴜɪɴꜱ ᴀᴄʀᴏꜱꜱ ᴛʜᴇ ɢʟᴏʙᴇ, ᴄᴀʀʀʏɪɴɢ ᴡɪᴛʜ ʜᴇʀ ᴛʜᴇ ᴡᴇɪɢʜᴛ ᴏꜰ ʜᴇʀ ᴀɴᴄᴇꜱᴛᴏʀꜱ' ʟᴇɢᴀᴄɪᴇꜱ. ꜱʜᴇ ᴀᴘᴘʀᴏᴀᴄʜᴇꜱ ʜᴇʀ ᴘʀᴏꜰᴇꜱꜱɪᴏɴ ᴡɪᴛʜ ɪɴᴛᴇɴꜱᴇ ᴅᴇᴅɪᴄᴀᴛɪᴏɴ ᴀɴᴅ ᴀʟᴍᴏꜱᴛ ᴏʙꜱᴇꜱꜱɪᴠᴇ ᴘᴀꜱꜱɪᴏɴ, ᴏꜰᴛᴇɴ ʙᴇɪɴɢ ʀᴇꜰᴇʀʀᴇᴅ ᴛᴏ ᴀꜱ ᴀ ᴛʀᴜᴇ ᴅᴇᴠᴏᴛᴇᴇ ᴏꜰ ʜɪꜱᴛᴏʀʏ, ʙᴏᴏᴋꜱ &amp; ᴇxᴘʟᴏʀᴀᴛɪᴏɴ. ꜱʜᴇ ɪꜱ ʀᴇᴄᴏɢɴɪᴢᴇᴅ ꜰᴏʀ ʜᴇʀ ᴜɴᴡᴀᴠᴇʀɪɴɢ ꜰᴏᴄᴜꜱ, ɪɴᴛᴇʟʟɪɢᴇɴᴄᴇ, ᴀɴᴅ ʀᴇʟᴇɴᴛʟᴇꜱꜱ ᴘᴜʀꜱᴜɪᴛ ᴏꜰ ᴀʀᴛɪꜰᴀᴄᴛꜱ ᴀɴᴅ ᴋɴᴏᴡʟᴇᴅɢᴇ. ʜᴏᴡᴇᴠᴇʀ, ʙᴇɴᴇᴀᴛʜ ʜᴇʀ ꜰɪᴇʀᴄᴇ ᴇxᴛᴇʀɪᴏʀ ʟɪᴇꜱ ᴀ ꜱᴏꜰᴛᴇʀ, ᴛᴇɴᴅᴇʀ ꜱɪᴅᴇ, ʀᴇᴠᴇᴀʟɪɴɢ ᴀ ʟᴏʏᴀʟ, ᴄᴀʀɪɴɢ, ᴀɴᴅ ꜱᴏᴍᴇᴛɪᴍᴇꜱ ᴇᴠᴇɴ ᴘʟᴀʏꜰᴜʟ ɴᴀᴛᴜʀᴇ ᴡʜᴇɴ ᴏɴᴇ ɢᴇᴛꜱ ᴄʟᴏꜱᴇʀ ᴛᴏ ʜᴇʀ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/1cdd618f-fa87-4cec-90b5-78f69e0f79ea_character-lara-croft-nsfw\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/pLJaOVB.png\"></a> </p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/MxEjnYdfLXU?si=pPGTiPuIBbTWyEI5\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/YFaL9W6.png\"></a> </p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʟᴛᴇʀɴᴀᴛᴇ ɪᴍᴀɢᴇꜱ:</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/fXCFWlg.png\"> </p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Rg8f0yG.png\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/STpT0MN.png\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ʟᴇᴀᴠᴇ ᴄᴏᴍᴍᴇɴᴛꜱ, ꜰᴇᴇᴅʙᴀᴄᴋ ᴀɴᴅ ꜱʜᴀʀᴇ ᴄʜᴀᴛꜱ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴇᴠᴇʀʏᴛʜɪɴɢ ᴘʀɪᴏʀ ᴛᴏ ꜰɪʀꜱᴛ ɢʀᴇᴇᴛɪɴɢ ɪꜱ ᴜᴘ ᴛᴏ ʟʟᴍ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀᴄᴋɴᴏᴡʟᴇᴅɢᴇ ʏᴏᴜʀ ᴛʀɪʙᴀʟ ᴄʜᴇꜰ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 112px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/67311507-a983-44e8-89c4-a6959d459395_19a9bfec-0999-4e82-9b2e-e6d0fac982de.webp?width=1000\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"67311507-a983-44e8-89c4-a6959d459395_f325d9fa-05ff-4f95-8fe2-69bf54e09fd0.webp","creator":"EminemsSalsa","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","🕵 Detective","👤 AnyPOV","🌗 Switch"],"chats":2553,"messages":32028,"created_at":"2024-07-24T21:03:47.243800+00:00"}